item.description:
Join NHCer Naim and friends for Karaoke tonight (Wednesday) at the Corner Pocket in Orange.

Group members plan to be there at 9:00 PM or a little before.

The Corner Pocket Cafe is a Pool Hall in Orange on the Boston Post Road.  They host Karaoke two nights a week, amongst various other events.

Naim will host this meetup so attempt to find him when you get there.  If it's too crowded or he's not in plain sight then he can be reached at 860-324-8780.

Thanks for hosting Naim!
item.how_to_find_us: Look for Naim (860-324-8780) or other member whom have RSVPed, it's not anticipated to be busy.
item.name: Karaoke at "The Corner Pocket Cafe"
